title: Overreactions to Overachievers | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 362)
description:
Justin Jackson and Ian Thomas lead this week's Initial Advice (01:30), and Dede Westbrook and Vernon Davis are among the top players to add off of waivers this week (10:00). Plus, overreactions to the wild week in fantasy, including Derrick Henry's and Amari Cooper's explosions, and Antonio Brown's and James White’s duds (23:00).

Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
